Name: prostatic urethral cancer
Definition: An embryonal testis carcinoma that occurs in children.

Name: obsolete Retroviridae infectious disease
Definition: A ssRNA-RT virus infectious disease that results_in infection in animals and humans

Name: penile urethral cancer
Definition: A fallopian tube adenofibroma that is characterized by the presence of cysts and/or cystic spaces.

Name: bulbomembranous urethral cancer
Definition: A rhinitis which is persistent and long-lasting. It may occur with diseases such as syphilis
Synonym: ureteral transitional cell carcinoma with squamous differentiation

Name: obsolete adenocarcinoma in adenomatous polyposis coli
Definition: A rhinitis which is persistent and long-lasting. It may occur with diseases such as syphilis
Synonym: adenocarcinoma in adenomatous polyposis coli (morphologic abnormality)
